    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You unleash a virulent disease on a creature that you can see within range. The target must make a [[/save]] save. On a failure, it takes [[/damage]] damage, or half as much damage on a success. The damage can’t reduce the target’s hit points below 1. If the target fails the save, its hit point maximum is reduced for 1 hour by an amount equal to the necrotic damage it took. Any effect that removes a disease allows a creature’s hit point maximum to return to normal before that time passes.</p>",
